The Glenn Beck Program - 10/11/13


Friday, October 11, 2013 11:16 AM


Did you hear about the dry run that a group of terrorists did on a domestic US flight?
  Didn't think so...

Glenn delves into the details.



Also, the future of the GOP, as well as another round of More On Trivia,

 Plus, TX congressman Louie Gohmert joins the show to discuss how the GOP is collapsing
 in the shutdown showdown against Obama.
